  <brief_title>Fluid Management After Surgery in the Post-Anesthetic Care Unit (PACU)</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Practice of Fluid Management in the Post-anesthetic Care Unit (PACU) of Shaare Zedek Medical Center in Patients Undergoing Elective Surgery: an Observational Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
